The world is building a corvette climax If China does not build this type of warship, will it lag behind?
With the recent announcement of the construction plan of new frigates by the world's major naval powers, it seems that the frigates have become the focus of attention of the navies of the major powers overnight, first Japan determined the purchase of two new frigates in the 2018 annual defense budget, which made the Japanese DEX frigate program finally have a substantial breakthrough, and then the United States Lockheed Martin recently announced the latest plan of the American FFG frigate program, so where should China's new frigates go?
With the launch of a latest Type 054A frigate at the end of 2017, it marks that as many as 29 054A frigates have been built, which is close to the sum of the 053H series frigates, and from the launch of the first 054A in 2006, the construction process of 054A has been 12 years, even in the world, the construction of such a large number of high-performance general-purpose frigates, in addition to China, there is only the United States built in the 7th and 80s of the last century "Perry" Class frigates can be compared.
And the reason why so many 054A are built is also very simple, that is, it is affordable, easy to use, and it is to supplement the Navy's arrears for many years.
054A frigate has been favored by the Chinese Navy for many years with its high cost performance and good combat effectiveness, its displacement of about 4000 tons, equipped with a 76 mm main gun, 32 units of Haihongqi-16 and Yu-8 anti-submarine missiles launched by the vertical system, 8 YJ-83 and a Zhi-9 helicopter, although it was built in 2006, the design time is a very early kind of ship, but its combat effectiveness is not too bad even today, looking at the frigates around the world can also reach the upper level.
But after all, this is a type of ship designed at the beginning of the 21st century, the weapon configuration aside, its power system and electronic radar equipment compared with the current mainstream frigates in the world There is already a big gap, like the same type of frigates in Europe has been equipped with all-electric propulsion, small multi-functional phased array radar, large-size helicopter deck, it is time to develop a new model.
So how China's new frigates should be developed is directly related to its future positioning and the strategic policy of our Chinese Navy.
The future development of the Chinese Navy will be completely a blue-water navy, and the future will also be to go to the ocean, with the ability to quickly deploy in areas closely related to China's vital interests, demonstrate the presence of force, and if necessary, have strong combat effectiveness to ensure that China's vital interests in the region are not damaged, then it seems that the new Hu Weijiang will inevitably develop towards large-scale and ocean-going development.
Looking at the positioning of the new frigate in the future sequence of the Chinese Navy, the future Chinese Navy should be similar to the US Navy, in addition to the necessary coastal defense ships, other capital ships will form an aircraft carrier battle group or amphibious assault ship strike group according to the needs of the situation.
The role of the new frigate in the future aircraft carrier battle group should be the main anti-submarine force and the positioning of the medium and near area emptying, and in the amphibious assault ship strike group should be used as a frigate, so according to such needs, the new frigate must have a strong anti-submarine capability and a good medium-range area airing capability.
Based on the above positioning, we can boldly envisage the approximate appearance of domestic frigates in the future.
First of all, the displacement will be greatly increased compared with the current Type 054A frigate, and it is estimated that the displacement of the new frigate will reach about 5000-6000 tons; The power system will use an integrated electric propulsion system composed of a QC280 improved gas turbine and two diesel engines, which is expected to reach a maximum speed of about 30 knots, and the endurance will also be greatly increased. As for the armament configuration, the 76 mm main gun and the 1130 close defense gun should be retained, but a Hongqi-10 launch system will be added, and there should be a 32-48 unit Hongqi-16 improved and Yu-8 co-frame vertical hair system behind the main gun, and a large vertical hair system of 8-16 units should be installed in the rear of the hull for launching YJ-18 and new cruise missiles; The hangar and parking platform will also be enlarged to accommodate two 10-ton helicopters; As for the electronic radar system, the high-end configuration should be equipped with a small four-sided fixed phased array radar based on the 346A, and the low-end configuration can use a multi-functional rotating phased array radar similar to that on European frigates.
In this way, the overall level of the new frigate will reach the current first-class level in the world, even compared with the American FFG.
Of course, the above concept is just the author's conjecture about the new domestic frigate, and we can only wait until the new frigate is launched to find out, so let's look forward to it.
